<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>ChillingCoffee Reset Password</title>

    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
</head>

<body
    style="margin: 0; padding: 0; min-width: 100%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; background-color: #FAFAFA; color: #222222;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div style="background-color: rgba(75,61,35,1); padding: 24px; color: #ffffff; text-align: center;">
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
                <img src="client/public/icon.ico" alt="ChillingCoffee Logo"
                    style="width: 50px; height: 50px; margin-right: 10px;">
                <h1
                    style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; color: #ffffff;">
                    Welcome to ChillingCoffee</h1>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div style="padding: 24px; background-color: #ffffff;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Hello {{name}},</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">You have requested to reset your password for ChillingCoffee. To
                reset your
                password, please use the following link:</p>
            <h2
                style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{resetUrl}}">Reset Password</a>
            </h2>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">Please enter this link on the reset password page
                within the next
                5 minutes.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">If you did not request a password reset, please
                ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #f6f6f6; padding: 24px;">
            <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 24px;">
                If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact
                us at <a href="https://youtube.com/@hoidanit" target="_blank"
                    style="color: #000; text-decoration:none;">ChillingCoffee</a> or visit our my coffeehouse
                </a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>